#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:74
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:300
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:400
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:500
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:602
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:704
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:806
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:969
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:1071
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:1166
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:1261
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:1358
msgid ""
"Instead of showing a CAPTCHA challenge, reCAPTCHA v3 returns a score so you "
"can choose the most appropriate action for your website. The score is based "
"on interactions with your site and enables you to take an appropriate "
"action for your site. reCaptcha will rank traffic and interactions based on "
"a score of 0.0 to 1.0, with a 1.0 being a good interaction and scores "
"closer to 0.0 indicating a good likelihood that the traffic was generated "
"by bots"
msgstr ""

#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:94
msgid "Note :- "
msgstr ""

#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:132
#: admin/includes/class-wbc-buddypress-settings-page.php:1414
msgid ""
"reCaptcha V3 does not show any challenge like I am not robot etc. reCaptcha "
"V3 uses a behind-the-scenes scoring system to detect abusive traffic, and "
"lets you decide the minimum passing score. Please note that there is no "
"user interaction shown in reRecapcha V3 meaning that no recaptcha challenge "
"is shown to solve."
msgstr ""

